---
title: Mushroom Quesadillas with Plant-Based Mozzarella, Lime Guacamole and Tomato Salad
description: These plant-based quesadillas are filled with Tex-Mex-flavoured mushrooms and spinach. Paired with a zippy lime guac and a fresh tomato salad, this dinner is totally craveable!
